text: We have an embedded form (JavaScript) on a HubSpot landing page. We are running a test on said landing page to see which converts higher. The form is connected via api to a HubSpot form but I’m not seeing the submission data come through on the results page of the test. Any ideas
When submitting the form, the records are created as expected in HubSpot, but the landing page test results don’t show any submissions happened on the page.
